text: Joe McCleery was an Irish football manager. He was the first manager of Derry City F.C. upon their entry into the Irish League in 1929. Prior to this he had been manager of Dundalk. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:Dundalk F.C. managers Category:Derry City F.C. managers Category:Republic of Ireland football managers
